                            <ul class="ml-3 mt-1 space-y-1 border-l-2 border-purple-500/30 pl-2">
                                <li><a href="#switch-case" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-blue-400 block">switch...case (+ multiple cases + default)</a></li>
